N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 485.12 - Contractual agreements

State Regulations

Current collective bargaining agreements may contain
provisions dealing with the content of this Part. Therefore, this Part should
be read in conjunction with those current collective bargaining agreements. These current agreements would supersede the content of this Part only in a
specific instance of such a conflict. Notes
